    "This is particularly relevant to inquiries that necessitate reasoning, abstract thought, and an appreciation of multiple perspectives.• Language models like LLMs have the potential to be effectively utilized for both few-shot and zero-shot learning (e.g.",
    "This advantage enables them to learn from limited labeled data and generalize well to new data, leading to numerous possibilities for practical application in the real world.• In this analysis, I took a high-level approach to examining the failures of ChatGPT.",
    "However, for future investigations, it may be useful to focus on more specific categories of problems, such as sentiment analysis, named entity recognition, translation [27,28], summarization [66], and language ambiguity [47], in order to gain a more detailed understanding of ChatGPT's shortcomings in these areas [49].• The integration of LLMs with search engines and the combination of answers from various chatbots, such as ChatGPT and Google's Bard, presents a non-trivial challenge.",
    "This is an issue that must be addressed in the future.• Making large language models open source can aid in gaining a deeper comprehension of these models and addressing their deficiencies.",
    "In a recent effort in this direction, Meta company has recently released the LLaMA model."
